oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Wrestling Team
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Wrestling; Wrestlers; Students; Athletes; Coaches (Athletics);
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Christian Brothers College's Wrestling team, circa 1935. Top Row (L-R): Assistant Coach Charles Foppiano, unknown, George Holeas, unknown, John Cavallo, unknown, Head Coach George Johnson. Middle Row (L-R): John Fravega, Anthony deFrances, Sylvio Lucchesi, George Griesbeck, unknown, Gene Laurenzi, George Mount, George Green. Bottom Row (L-R): Frank Sampietro, unknown, George McElwaine, James Sheridan, Joe Gangi.
